data.description: Afghanistan administrative level 0-2 boundaries (COD-AB) dataset. Sourced from Afghanistan Geodesy and Cartography Head Office (AGCHO) This COD-AB is suitable for database or GIS linkage to the Afghanistan [COD-PS](https://data.humdata.org/dataset/cod-ps-afg). No edge-matched (COD-EM) version of this COD-AB has yet been prepared. Please see the [COD Portal](https://cod.unocha.org/). Administrative level 1 contains 34 feature(s). The normal administrative level 1 feature type is 'Province'. Administrative level 2 contains 401 feature(s). The normal administrative level 2 feature type is 'District'.
